text.__SUMMARY__: Shorea domatiosa is a species of plant in the Dipterocarpaceae family.   It is endemic to Borneo. It is an Endangered species threatened by habitat loss.
text.Sources: Ashton, P. (1998). "Shorea domatiosa". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T33410A9781251. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33410A9781251.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
